flavour_text:
The larger its
petals, the more
toxic pollen it contains. Its big
head is heavy and
hard to hold up.
name: vileplume

flavour_text:
Nuota velocissimo usando tutti i muscoli.
Riesce persino a battere atleti di caratura
mondiale.
name: poliwrath

flavour_text:
The plant blooms
when it is
absorbing solar energy. It stays
on the move to
seek sunlight.
name: venusaur

flavour_text:
Spits fire that
is hot enough to
melt boulders. Known to cause
forest fires
unintentionally.
name: charizard

flavour_text:
A brutal POKéMON
with pressurized
water jets on its shell. They are
used for high
speed tackles.
name: blastoise

flavour_text:
In battle, it
flaps its wings
at high speed to release highly
toxic dust into
the air.
name: butterfree

flavour_text:
It has three poisonous stingers on its forelegs and
its tail. They are used to jab its enemy repeatedly.
name: beedrill

flavour_text:
When hunting, it
skims the surface
of water at high speed to pick off
unwary prey such
as MAGIKARP.
name: pidgeot

flavour_text:
Its long tail
serves as a
ground to protect itself from its
own high voltage
power.
name: raichu

flavour_text:
Its hard scales
provide strong
protection. It uses its hefty
bulk to execute
powerful moves.
name: nidoqueen

flavour_text:
It uses its
powerful tail in
battle to smash, constrict, then
break the prey's
bones.
name: nidoking

flavour_text:
A timid fairy
POKéMON that is
rarely seen. It will run and hide
the moment it
senses people.
name: clefable

flavour_text:
Il suo corpo è morbido e gommoso. Se si arrabbia,
aspira aria e si gonfia enormemente.
name: wigglytuff

flavour_text:
Su cerebro puede ganar al de un ordenador de alta
gama. Tiene un coeficiente intelectual de 5000.
name: alakazam

flavour_text:
Using its heavy
muscles, it throws
powerful punches that can send the
victim clear over
the horizon.
name: machamp

flavour_text:
Said to live in
huge colonies
deep in jungles, although no one
has ever returned
from there.
name: victreebel

flavour_text:
Its boulder-like
body is extremely
hard. It can easily withstand
dynamite blasts
without damage.
name: golem

flavour_text:
Under a full moon,
this POKéMON
likes to mimic the shadows of
people and laugh
at their fright.
name: gengar

flavour_text:
An extremely
rarely seen
marine POKéMON. Its intelligence
is said to match
that of humans.
name: dragonite

flavour_text:
Son souffle a l’incroyable capacité
de ranimer les plantes et les fleurs
flétries.
name: meganium

flavour_text:
If its rage peaks,
it becomes so hot
that anything that touches it will
instantly go
up in flames.
name: typhlosion

flavour_text:
When it bites with
its massive and
powerful jaws, it shakes its head
and savagely tears
its victim up.
name: feraligatr

flavour_text:
It flies so si­
lently through the
dark on its four wings that it may
not be noticed
even when nearby.
name: crobat

flavour_text:
The tail's tip
shines brightly
and can be seen from far away. It
acts as a beacon
for lost people.
name: ampharos

flavour_text:
BELLOSSOM gather
at times and
appear to dance. They say that the
dance is a ritual
to summon the sun.
name: bellossom

flavour_text:
By keeping still
and listening in­
tently, it can tell what is in
even wild, fast-
moving rivers.
name: azumarill

flavour_text:
It is said that it usually hides in
underwater caves. It can create
whirlpools by yawning.
name: kingdra

flavour_text:
If POLIWAG and
POLIWHIRL hear its
echoing cry, they respond by gather­
ing from far and
wide.
name: politoed

flavour_text:
Este amable Pokémon cuida de Pokémon enfermos y
los sana. Puede percibir la tristeza.
name: blissey

flavour_text:
Blown by seasonal winds, it
circles the globe, scattering
cotton spores as it goes.
name: jumpluff

flavour_text:
Its body can't be
harmed by any sort
of attack, so it is very eager to
make challenges
against enemies.
name: tyranitar

flavour_text:
The leaves growing on SCEPTILE’s body
are very sharp edged. This POKéMON is
very agile - it leaps all over the branches of trees and jumps on its foe
from above or behind.
name: sceptile

flavour_text:
In battle, BLAZIKEN blows out intense
flames from its wrists and attacks foes
courageously. The stronger the foe, the more
intensely this POKéMON’s wrists burn.
name: blaziken

flavour_text:
Con sus brazos duros como el acero puede partir
rocas gigantescas en mil pedazos de un solo golpe.
name: swampert

flavour_text:
BEAUTIFLY’s favorite food is the sweet
pollen of flowers. If you want to see
this POKéMON, just leave a potted flower by an open window. BEAUTIFLY
is sure to come looking for pollen.
name: beautifly

flavour_text:
CASCOON makes its protective cocoon
by wrapping its body entirely with a
fine silk from its mouth. Once the silk goes around its body, it hardens.
This POKéMON prepares for its evolution
inside the cocoon.
name: cascoon

flavour_text:
LUDICOLO begins dancing as soon as
it hears cheerful, festive music.
This POKéMON is said to appear when it hears the singing of children on hiking
outings.
name: ludicolo

flavour_text:
SHIFTRY is a mysterious POKéMON that
is said to live atop towering trees
dating back over a thousand years. It creates terrific windstorms with
the fans it holds.
name: shiftry

flavour_text:
GARDEVOIR has the ability to read the
future. If it senses impending danger
to its TRAINER, this POKéMON is said to unleash its psychokinetic energy at
full power.
name: gardevoir

flavour_text:
SLAKING spends all day lying down and
lolling about.
It eats grass growing within its reach. If it eats all the grass it can reach,
this POKéMON reluctantly moves to
another spot.
name: slaking

flavour_text:
EXPLOUD triggers earthquakes with the
tremors it creates by bellowing. If this
POKéMON violently inhales from the ports on its body, it’s a sign that it is
preparing to let loose a huge bellow.
name: exploud

flavour_text:
AGGRON claims an entire mountain as its
own territory. It mercilessly beats up
anything that violates its environment. This POKéMON vigilantly patrols its
territory at all times.
name: aggron

flavour_text:
FLYGON is nicknamed “the elemental
spirit of the desert.” Because its
flapping wings whip up a cloud of sand, this POKéMON is always enveloped in a
sandstorm while flying.
name: flygon

flavour_text:
WALREIN’s two massively developed
tusks can totally shatter blocks of
ice weighing ten tons with one blow. This POKéMON’s thick coat of blubber
insulates it from subzero temperatures.
name: walrein

flavour_text:
Il suo intenso desiderio di volare ha provocato
una mutazione cellulare che ha fatto nascere le
tanto agognate ali.
name: salamence

flavour_text:
METAGROSS has four brains in total.
Combined, the four brains can breeze
through difficult calculations faster than a supercomputer.
This POKéMON can float in the air by
tucking in its four legs.
name: metagross

flavour_text:
Algunos Pokémon pequeños se juntan en su espalda
para hacer sus nidos.
name: torterra

flavour_text:
It uses a special kind of martial
arts involving all its limbs.
Its fire never goes out.
name: infernape

flavour_text:
It has a savage nature. It will
courageously challenge foes that
are much larger.
name: staraptor

flavour_text:
It attracts prey with a sweet
aroma, then downs it with
thorny whips hidden in its arms.
name: roserade

flavour_text:
It evolved from exposure to a
special magnetic field.
Three units generate magnetism.
name: magnezone

flavour_text:
It puts rocks in holes in its palms
and uses its muscles to shoot them.
GEODUDE are shot at rare times.
name: rhyperior

flavour_text:
The three horns that extend from
its beak attest to its power. The
leader has the biggest horns.
name: empoleon

flavour_text:
It pushes the tips of its two tails
against the foe, then lets loose
with over 20,000 volts of power.
name: electivire

flavour_text:
It blasts fireballs of over 3,600
degrees F from the ends of its
arms. It lives in volcanic craters.
name: magmortar

flavour_text:
It will never appear where there
is strife. Its sightings have
become rare recently.
name: togekiss

flavour_text:
Its impressive tusks are made of
ice. The population thinned when it
turned warm after the ice age.
name: mamoswine

flavour_text:
Non sembra funzionare correttamente dopo essere stato
riprogrammato per muoversi in dimensioni sconosciute.
name: porygon-z

flavour_text:
A master of courtesy and
swordsmanship, it fights using
extending swords on its elbows.
name: gallade

flavour_text:
The antenna on its head captures
radio waves from the world of spirits
that command it to take people there.
name: dusknoir

flavour_text:
It has eyes that can see through
anything. It spots and captures
prey hiding behind objects.
name: luxray

flavour_text:
When it folds up its body and
extends its wings, it looks like a
jet plane. It flies at sonic speed.
name: garchomp

flavour_text:
Il peut paralyser l’ennemi d’un regard.
Il amplifie l’énergie du soleil dans
son corps.
name: serperior

flavour_text:
It has mastered fast and powerful fighting moves.
It grows a beard of fire.
name: emboar

flavour_text:
Il peut terrasser ses ennemis d’un coup
de la lame enchâssée dans son armure,
et les faire taire d’un seul regard.
name: samurott

flavour_text:
Il sauve les gens bloqués dans les
montagnes par des tempêtes de neige.
Ses longs poils le protègent du froid.
name: stoutland

flavour_text:
Le mâle intimide ses ennemis
avec ses caroncules.
La femelle vole mieux que le mâle.
name: unfezant

flavour_text:
Il comprime de l’énergie dans son corps,
et ses attaques sont assez puissantes
pour renverser des montagnes.
name: gigalith

flavour_text:
On pense que la recette du ciment
a été enseignée aux humains par
un Bétochef il y a 2 000 ans.
name: conkeldurr

flavour_text:
Il fait gicler un liquide paralysant des
pustules sur sa tête, et attaque
ses ennemis à coups de vibrations.
name: seismitoad

flavour_text:
Quand il trouve de petits Pokémon, il
leur coud des vêtements de feuilles en
utilisant ses coupoirs et son fil adhésif.
name: leavanny

flavour_text:
Il ne laisse jamais échapper ses proies.
Ses mâchoires surpuissantes peuvent
broyer une voiture.
name: krookodile

flavour_text:
Il accule l’ennemi par ses mouvements
rapides et l’attaque avec ses cornes.
Il ne s’arrête qu’au coup de grâce.
name: scolipede

flavour_text:
すさまじい　せいりょうを　もつ。
シャウトとともに　いかくするさまは
ブロッキングと　よばれている。
name: obstagoon

flavour_text:
タップダンスの　たつじん。
こおりで　できた　ステッキを　ふり
かろやかな　ステップを　ひろうする。
name: mr-rime

flavour_text:
Ses pouvoirs psychiques plient l’espace
aux alentours. On y voit des étoiles
éloignées de millions d’années-lumière.
name: gothitelle

flavour_text:
Quand ils se tiennent par la main,
leurs cerveaux forment un réseau qui
démultiplie leurs pouvoirs psychiques.
name: reuniclus

flavour_text:
The gear with the red core is rotated at high speed
for a rapid energy charge.
name: klinklang

flavour_text:
Il peut sortir de l’eau à la force de ses
bras pour attraper des proies sur la
rive. Il retourne à l’eau en un instant.
name: eelektross

flavour_text:
Il brûle en aspirant les âmes, et
hypnotise ses ennemis en faisant
osciller les flammes de ses bras.
name: chandelure

flavour_text:
Il est doux, mais ne pardonne pas à ceux
qui viennent saccager son territoire.
Ses crocs peuvent découper de l’acier.
name: haxorus

flavour_text:
Un Pokémon violent qui patrouille le ciel
avec ses six ailes et se jette sur tout
ce qui bouge, pensant voir un ennemi.
name: hydreigon

flavour_text:
たいあたりで　５０トンの　せんしゃを
ひっくりかえす　パワー。じぶんが
たてと　なって　なかまを　まもる。
name: chesnaught

flavour_text:
みずを　あっしゅくして　しゅりけんを
つくりだす。こうそくかいてんさせて
とばすと　きんぞくも　まっぷたつ。
name: greninja

flavour_text:
主要以鸟宝可梦为食。
会从羽毛的缝隙里
喷出火花来威吓对手。
name: talonflame

flavour_text:
せかいには　さまざまな　はねもようの
ビビヨンがいる。すんでいる　とちの
きこうが　えいきょうしているようだ。
name: vivillon

flavour_text:
Il avale de l’eau en grande quantité
et la transforme en nuages neigeux.
Il souffle du blizzard sur ses ennemis.
name: vanilluxe

flavour_text:
Habita en preciosos jardines floridos. Absorbe la
energía que emiten las plantas y la convierte en su
fuente de poder.
name: florges

flavour_text:
つえの　せんたんで　もえる　ほのおを
みつめて　せいしんとういつすると
みらいの　できごとを　みとおせる。
name: delphox

flavour_text:
れきだいの　おうが　つれていた。
れいりょくで　ひとや　ポケモンの
こころを　あやつり　したがわせる。
name: aegislash-shield

flavour_text:
ひとなつっこい　ドラゴンポケモン。
だいすきな　トレーナーに　だきついて
ねんえきで　ヌルヌルにしてしまう。
name: goodra

flavour_text:
つばさに　しこまれた　やばねを
つがえてはなつ。　１００メートルさきの
こいしも　つらぬく　せいど。
name: decidueye

flavour_text:
そぼうで　みがってな　せいかく。
きぶんが　のらなければ　トレーナーの
めいれいも　へいきで　むしするぞ。
name: incineroar

flavour_text:
クチバシを　はつねつさせ　たたかう。
そのおんどは　１００どを　ゆうに　こえ
つつかれるだけで　おおやけど。
name: toucannon

flavour_text:
とびまわって　スキを　うかがう。
でんきエネルギーを　おおきなアゴで
しゅうそくさせ　てきに　はっしゃ。
name: vikavolt

flavour_text:
あしを　いかした　けりが　とくい。
たおした　あいてを　あしげに　して
たかわらいで　しょうりを　アピール。
name: tsareena

flavour_text:
てきを　みると　しっぽの　ウロコを
ジャラジャラ　ならして　いかく。
よわいものは　あわてて　にげだす。
name: kommo-o

flavour_text:
とくべつな　きりかぶの　パワーを
ドラミングで　コントロール。
ねっこを　あやつって　たたかう。
name: rillaboom

flavour_text:
こいしを　リフティングして　ほのおの
サッカーボールを　つくる。　するどい
シュートで　あいてを　もやす。
name: cinderace

flavour_text:
たさいな　きのうを　かくしもつ。
ゆびから　みずを　ふんしゃして
せなかの　ひまくで　かぜに　のる。
name: inteleon

flavour_text:
ガラルちほうの　そらでは　てきなし。
くろびかりする　はがねの　すがたは
あいてを　いあつし　おそれさせる。
name: corviknight

flavour_text:
かしこい　ポケモンとして　ゆうめい。
おおきな　のうみそは　きょうりょくな
サイコパワーを　もつ　あかし。
name: orbeetle

flavour_text:
ふだんは　おだやかだが　にんげんが
こうざんを　あらすと　いかりくるい
１５００どの　ほのおで　やきつくす。
name: coalossal

flavour_text:
かみのけを　ぜんしんに　まきつけると
きんりょくが　アップ。　カイリキーを
ねじふせる　パワーを　はっきする。
name: grimmsnarl

flavour_text:
ツノの　あなに　ドラメシヤを　いれて
くらす。　たたかいになると　マッハの
スピードで　ドラメシヤを　とばす。
name: dragapult

flavour_text:
みずのバルーンを　うたで　あやつる。
そのメロディは　なかまに　まなび
だいだい　むれに　ひきつがれていく。
name: primarina

flavour_text:
ずつうになるほどの　サイコパワーを
しゅういに　はなって　ほかの
せいぶつを　とおざけているのだ。
name: hatterene
